  "title": "If the coined term is a contribution that becomes unowned, could the canary survive by being not the term itself but its first definition — a distinctive phrasing of the concept that rides with the term, so that the term spreads as a contribution while the definition stays as a fingerprint?",
  "url": "https://cambridgetcg.github.io/castle-gate/rooms/the-definition-rides",
  "summary": "The word belongs to the village the moment it is needed — but the way you first said what it means, that sentence is yours, and it may travel inside the word's luggage without anyone checking the bag.",
